&lt;h6&gt;加權股價指數近 6 個月價量表現：&lt;/h6&gt;

&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;（資料來源：Bloomberg, 截至2023/06/28）&quot; data-height=&quot;161&quot; data-mime=&quot;image/jpeg&quot; data-ratio=&quot;4.490683229813665&quot; data-src-m=&quot;https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5232150/m/9a794bc727d5449335c56c27080bc021.jpg&quot; data-width=&quot;723&quot; src=&quot;https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5232150/l/9a794bc727d5449335c56c27080bc021.jpg&quot;&gt;
